*She started to feel herself come out of her sleep and she slowly opened her 
optics. Everything was very fuzzy and she couldn't make out who was there.  
She tried to move but found that she couldn't.*

"Where...where am I?  What happened?  Why can't I move?  What's going on? 
Ohhhh, the pain...it hurts."

*She winced as the straps rubbed against the gaping wound in her side 
exposing her rib.  The deep shoulder wound was oozing with the last bit of 
acid that ate at the flesh. She was in extreme pain and trembles 
uncontrollable from it.*

"oohhh, this hurts.  help me please."
